

=Bio=

"I’m a two-years master student in Economics at University of Turin, Italy, and I’m about to finish my studies.

I’m well-versed in statistical methods for data analysis and I am passionate about research done with micro data sets.

I’m currently preparing my master thesis doing a research about investors on [[Equity-Based Crowdfunding]] in Europe. 

In order to develop this analysis I’m currently doing an internship with an Anglo/Italian research-led business."



